    <abstract>
      <t>This specification defines the WebFinger protocol, which can be used to discover information about people or other entities on the Internet using standard HTTP methods.  WebFinger discovers information for a URI that might not be usable as a locator otherwise, such as account or email URIs.
	 </t>
